snippet.title: Amzi's True Tea & Crime
snippet.description:
Hey my name is Amy but everyone call me Amzi (and everyone pronounces it different don't feel bad) 
I focus my channel mainly on true crime, missing persons cases. I originally started getting the channel popping on covering MTV reality TV shows, like Teen Mom OG, Teen Mom 2, and Young and pregnant I covered 2020 16 and pregnant, and I use to dabble in Jersey shore, now while I still sprinkle that among my channel from time to time, our main goal is now to find missing persons, children and find justice for their loved ones. 
reach out to me via the info below outside of YouTube. 
One Love 

Twitter: @amzibeloved
Instagram: @amzibeloved
email: amzibeloved@gmail.com
